{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Value to use for a text label."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSExpression","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"text"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Within a constant string value, a feature attribute name enclosed in curly"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"braces (e.g., "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"{token}"},{"type":"text","text":") is replaced with the value of the named attribute."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Tokens inside non-constant expressions are ignored; instead, use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"mgl_join:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and key path expressions."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is an expression that evaluates to the empty"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"string. Set this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" to reset it to the default value."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This attribute corresponds to the "},{"type":"text","text":"text-field"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layout property in the MapLibre Style Spec."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","tex